INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("674","1","2013-05-16 03:50:33","2013-05-16 03:50:33","The Widgetkit Media Player is a HTML5 audio and video player completely built HTML and CSS. You can easily embed video files into your website by using the HTML5 video element. A Flash player fallback is included for all unsupported browsers.\n<h2>Features</h2>\n<ul class=\"check\">\n	<li>Native playback for modern HTML5 browsers</li>\n	<li>Supports MP4 (h.264), WebM, FLV, WMV and MP3 files</li>\n	<li>Completely built with HTML and CSS</li>\n	<li>Responsive design to fit all device resolutions</li>\n	<li>Same UI in all browsers</li>\n	<li>Create your own skins</li>\n	<li>Flash player fallback for unsupported browsers</li>\n	<li>Works with Joomla and WordPress</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Examples</h2>\n<video width=\"640\" height=\"360\" poster=\"http://www.yootheme.com/videos/mediaplayer.jpg\" controls=\"controls\" preload=\"none\"><source src=\"http://www.yootheme.com/videos/mediaplayer.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" /><object width=\"640\" height=\"360\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://localhost:8888/nasl-concept/wp-includes/js/tinymce/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf\" /><param name=\"flashvars\" value=\"url=http%3A//www.yootheme.com/videos/mediaplayer.mp4&amp;poster=http%3A//www.yootheme.com/videos/mediaplayer.jpg\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"true\" /><embed width=\"640\" height=\"360\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/nasl-concept/wp-includes/js/tinymce/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf\" flashvars=\"url=http%3A//www.yootheme.com/videos/mediaplayer.mp4&amp;poster=http%3A//www.yootheme.com/videos/mediaplayer.jpg\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowscriptaccess=\"true\" /></object>\n\n</video>\n\nThis is a MP3 Audio Sample:\n\n<audio width=\"300\" height=\"32\" src=\"http://www.yootheme.com/videos/mediaplayer.mp3\" type=\"audio/mp3\" controls=\"controls\" preload=\"none\"></audio>\n<h2>How To Use</h2>\nUse the HTML5 <code>video</code> element to embed video in your website. For example:\n<pre>&lt;video src=\"/video.mp4\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\"&gt;&lt;/video&gt;</pre>\nYou can also provide multiple sources, to add support for the different video formats like h.264, WebM or Ogg:\n<pre>&lt;video width=\"320\" height=\"240\"&gt;\n	&lt;source type=\"video/mp4\"  src=\"/video.mp4\" /&gt;\n	&lt;source type=\"video/webm\" src=\"/video.webm\" /&gt;\n	&lt;source type=\"video/ogg\"  src=\"/video.ogv\" /&gt;\n&lt;/video&gt;</pre>\nUse the HTML5 <code>audio</code> element to embed MP3 files in your website. For example:\n<pre>&lt;audio src=\"/audio.mp3\" type=\"audio/mp3\"&gt;&lt;/audio&gt;</pre>","Media Player","","inherit","open","open","","117-autosave","","","2013-05-16 03:50:33","2013-05-16 03:50:33","","117","http://localhost:8888/nasl-concept/?p=674","0","revision","","0");
